msgctxt "1096"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "84_Gossipy Woman"
msgid "Their yakiniku's great and all, but the kimchi here is out of this world."
msgstr "El yakiniku de aquí es rico, pero su kimchi es realmente delicioso."

msgctxt "96_Rich Foodie"
msgid "I know. I heard all about it the last time I was at the hostess club."
msgstr "Lo sé, escuché el rumor la última vez que fui a un cabaret."

msgctxt "108_Gossipy Woman"
msgid "...A hostess club, huh?"
msgstr "¿Un cabaret?"

msgctxt "120_Rich Foodie"
msgid "No, I meant the hostless club? No hosts in sight there, lemme tell you that! Anyway, uh, let's go eat! My treat!"
msgstr "No, no... Ca-café, me refería a un café. Vamos, entremos."

msgctxt "132_Gossipy Woman"
msgid "Sure. While we're there, we can talk all about that \"hostless\" club you went to."
msgstr "Sí. Podrás contarme sobre ese \"café\" al que fuiste."

